    personalityTraits: ['I judge people by their actions, not their words.', 'If someone is in trouble, I\'m always ready to lend help.', 'When I set my mind to something, I follow through no matter what gets in my way.', 'I have a strong sense of fair play and always try to find the most equitable solution to arguments.'],
