    personalityTraits: ['I\'m always polite and respectful.', 'I\'m haunted by memories of war. I wake up screaming in the night.', 'I\'ve lost too many friends, and I\'m slow to make new ones.', 'I\'m full of inspiring and cautionary tales from my military experience relevant to almost every combat situation.'],
