    personalityTraits: ['I\'m driven by a wanderlust that led me away from home.', 'I watch over my friends as if they were a litter of newborn pups.', 'I once ran twenty-five miles without stopping to warn my clan of an approaching orc horde.', 'I have a lesson for every situation, drawn from observing nature.'],
