    bonds: ['My family, clan, or tribe is the most important thing in my life, even when they are far from me.', 'An injury to the unspoiled wilderness of my home is an injury to me.', 'I will bring terrible wrath down on the evildoers who destroyed my homeland.'],
    flaws: ['I am too enamored of ale, wine, and other intoxicants.', 'There\'s no room for caution in a life lived to the fullest.', 'I remember every insult I\'ve received and nurse a silent resentment toward anyone who\'s ever wronged me.'],
