    personalityTraits: ['I\'ve been isolated for so long that I rarely speak, preferring gestures and the occasional grunt.', 'I am utterly serene, even in the face of disaster.', 'The leader of my community had something wise to say on every topic, and I am eager to share that wisdom.', 'I feel tremendous empathy for all who suffer.'],
