    personalityTraits: ['I hide scraps of food and trinkets away in my pockets.', 'I ask a lot of questions.', 'I like to squeeze into small places where no one else can get to me.', 'I sleep with my back to a wall or tree, with everything I own wrapped in a bundle in my arms.'],
